graph TD
    A[Start: Client lacks access to affordable childcare]

    A --> B{Do the children have special needs or chronic health issues?}
    B --> B1[Yes]
    B1 --> C{Are specialized childcare services available?}
    C --> C1[Yes]
    C1 --> D[Connect client with specialized providers; assist with applications]
    C --> C2[No]
    C2 --> E[Explore in-home care or financial assistance options]

    B --> B2[No]
    B2 --> F{What are the ages of the children?}
    F --> F1[Under school age]
    F1 --> G{Are free/subsidized pre-K programs available?}
    G --> G1[Yes]
    G1 --> H[Assist in enrolling children in pre-K programs]
    G --> G2[No]
    G2 --> I[Explore other childcare options]

    F --> F2[School-aged]
    F2 --> J{Are children enrolled in school?}
    J --> J1[Yes]
    J1 --> K{Is before/after school care needed?}
    K --> K1[Yes]
    K1 --> L{Are school-based programs available?}
    L --> L1[Yes]
    L1 --> M[Assist in enrolling in school-based care]
    L --> L2[No]
    L2 --> N[Explore community programs]
    K --> K2[No]
    K2 --> O[Focus on work during school hours]
    J --> J2[No]
    J2 --> P[Assist with school enrollment]

    F --> F3[Mixed ages]
    F3 --> Q[Address needs based on individual ages]

    I & N --> R{Are immediate family/friends available for childcare?}
    R --> R1[Yes]
    R1 --> S{Is the care reliable and covers work hours?}
    S --> S1[Yes]
    S1 --> T[Leverage support; create a schedule]
    S --> S2[No]
    S2 --> U[Identify gaps; explore backup options]

    R --> R2[No]
    R2 --> V{Is the client eligible for childcare assistance programs?}
    V --> V1[Yes]
    V1 --> W[Assist with applications for subsidies/programs]
    V --> V2[No]
    V2 --> X{Are there local non-profit/community childcare services?}
    X --> X1[Yes]
    X1 --> Y[Connect client with resources]
    X --> X2[No]
    X2 --> Z{Is client open to childcare cooperative with other parents?}
    Z --> Z1[Yes]
    Z1 --> AA[Facilitate joining/forming a cooperative]
    Z --> Z2[No]
    Z2 --> AB{Is remote work from home a viable option?}

    AB --> AB1[Yes]
    AB1 --> AC{Does client have skills for remote work?}
    AC --> AC1[Yes]
    AC1 --> AD[Explore remote job opportunities]
    AC --> AC2[No]
    AC2 --> AE[Identify training programs for remote work skills]
    AB --> AB2[No]
    AB2 --> AF{Can client work flexible/part-time hours?}
    AF --> AF1[Yes]
    AF1 --> AG[Identify jobs with flexible scheduling]
    AF --> AF2[No]
    AF2 --> AH{Is starting an in-home childcare business an option?}
    AH --> AH1[Yes]
    AH1 --> AI[Provide resources for starting home-based childcare]
    AH --> AH2[No]
    AH2 --> AJ[Explore financial assistance or grants for childcare costs]

    D & E & H & M & O & P & T & U & W & Y & AA & AD & AE & AG & AI & AJ --> END[End: Tailored Action Plan addressing childcare obstacles]
